OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fdry evening with plenty of late
OL,7,Fsunshine. Overnight will stay
OL,8,Fgenerally dry and clear. A low risk of
OL,9,Fan isolated thundery shower to the far
OL,10,Fsouthwest. A warm night to come,
OL,11,Fespecially in the towns and cities.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FAnother hot day on Tuesday,
OL,14,Falthough sunshine likely to be more
OL,15,Fhazy than recently. A small chance of
OL,16,Fthe odd shower in the west but most
OL,17,Fstaying dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
