OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FRemaining hot with plenty more
OL,7,Fsunshine, although an increasing risk
OL,8,Fof some showers and thunderstorms at
OL,9,Ftimes. Lighter winds than Monday and
OL,10,FTuesday adding to the hot feel.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
